@Service public class RiverTimestepMapCrudService extends AbstractBaseMapCrudService<RiverTimestep>
RiverTimestepMapCrudService is an implementation of the AbstractBaseMapCrudService class, providing CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for managing RiverTimestep objects. This service is annotated with Service to indicate that it is a Spring service component.
